cli.help.page.add_extension:
Pack extensionkunaman datuta yapay (provider extension ñanqa legacy/schema-core)

Imayna llamk'achiy: greentic-pack add-extension [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Kamachiykuna:
  provider    Provider extension yaykuyninta yapay utaq musuqyachiy
  capability  Capability offer yaykuyninta yapay utaq musuqyachiy

Akllanakuna:
  --locale <LOCALE>  CLI willakuykunapa locale
cli.help.page.add_extension_capability:
Capability offer yaykuyninta yapay utaq musuqyachiy

Imayna llamk'achiy: greentic-pack add-extension capability [OPTIONS] --pack-dir <DIR> --offer-id <ID> --cap-id <CAP_ID> --component-ref <COMPONENT> --op <OP>

Llapan argumento detallekunapaq `greentic-pack add-extension capability --help` nisqata llamk'achiy.
cli.help.page.add_extension_provider:
Provider extension yaykuyninta yapay utaq musuqyachiy

Imayna llamk'achiy: greentic-pack add-extension provider [OPTIONS] --pack-dir <DIR> --id <PROVIDER_ID> --kind <KIND>

Llapan argumento detallekunapaq `greentic-pack add-extension provider --help` nisqata llamk'achiy.

cli.help.page.root:
Greentic pack CLI

Imayna llamk'achiy: greentic-pack [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Kamachiykuna:
  build          Pack componentta yanapana artefactokunatawan ruray
  lint           Pack manifestta, flowkunata, templatekunatapas lint ruwachiy
  components     pack.yaml componentkunata components/ ukupi archivokunawan tinkichiy
  update         pack root ukhupi archivokunawan pack.yaml componentkunata flowkunatawan tinkichiy
  new            Musuq pack directorio paqarichiy
  sign           Ed25519 sapalla llaveyuqwan pack manifestta firmay
  verify         Packpa manifest firmaninta chiqaqchay
  gui            GUI-nisqaman tupaq herramientakuna
  doctor         Pack archivota (.gtpack) utaq fuente directoriota diagnostikay (validación purichin)
  inspect        `doctor`paq deprecado suti-rantin
  inspect-lock   pack.lock.cbor-ta qhaway (stdoutman takyasqa JSON)
  qa             Component QA-ta purichiy, kutichiykunatapas waqaychay
  config         Allichasqa configuraciónta qhaway (provenance, warningkunapas)
  plan           Pack archivomanta utaq fuente directoriomanta DeploymentPlan paqarichiy
  providers      Ñawpa provider-extension yanapakuykuna (schema-core ñan)
  add-extension  Pack extensionkunaman datuta yapay (provider extension ñanqa legacy/schema-core)
  wizard         Pack wizard yanapakuykuna
  resolve        Component referenciakunata allinchay, pack.lock.cbor-ta qillqay
